[I] Linux Containers

[T] LXC is the well-known and heavily tested low-level Linux container runtime.
[T] It is in active development since 2008 and has proven itself in critical
[T] production environments world-wide.

[U] https://github.com/lxc/lxc

[A] LXC Developers
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS

[E] opt docbook2x
[E] opt perl-sax-exception perl-sax-parser perl-xml-namespace-support

[L] GPL
[V] 7.0.0
